Excellent movie. Many messages here. Loved It!!!!!

a very nicely done family film with old favorites like robert vaughn and ron perlman, and a nice turn by mia sara. there is enough comedy and action to keep one's interest, and the violence is played for laughs. myles jefferies is a new up and coming comedic talent to watch for. he is wonderful as archie.
